# Multi-Modal RAG System

Production-grade RAG system supporting PDFs, images, and CSV data with hybrid search,
Cohere reranking, and an evaluation dashboard. Deployed on Azure Container Apps.

## Architecture

```
Upload (PDF / Image / CSV)
        │
        ├── PDF  → PyMuPDF → RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter
        ├── IMG  → GPT-4 Vision → caption text
        └── CSV  → row serialisation + stats chunk
                │
        OpenAI text-embedding-3-large (3072 dims)
                │
        Pinecone (3 namespaces: text | image | table)
                │
        Query → BM25 + Semantic → RRF Fusion → Cohere Rerank
                │
        GPT-4o → grounded answer + source citations + confidence
```

## Quick start

```bash
# 1. Clone & install
git clone <repo>
cd multimodal-rag
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2. Configure
cp .env.example .env
# Fill in OPENAI_API_KEY, PINECONE_API_KEY, COHERE_API_KEY

# 3. Run locally
streamlit run app.py
```

## Docker

```bash
docker build -t multimodal-rag .
docker run -p 8501:8501 --env-file .env multimodal-rag
```

## Azure deployment

```bash
az acr build --registry <your-registry> --image multimodal-rag:latest .

az deployment group create \
  --resource-group <rg> \
  --template-file azure-deploy.bicep \
  --parameters \
      containerImage=<your-registry>.azurecr.io/multimodal-rag:latest \
      openaiKey=$OPENAI_API_KEY \
      pineconeKey=$PINECONE_API_KEY \
      pineconeEnv=us-east-1 \
      cohereKey=$COHERE_API_KEY
```

## Key design decisions

| Choice | Why |
|--------|-----|
| Pinecone over ChromaDB | Managed, production-scale, namespace support for multi-modal |
| text-embedding-3-large | Best OpenAI retrieval quality (3072 dims) |
| BM25 + semantic (hybrid) | Covers both exact-match and semantic queries |
| RRF fusion | Parameter-free, robust rank combination |
| Cohere cross-encoder rerank | Re-scores top-20 with full query-document attention |
| GPT-4o Vision | State-of-art image understanding for caption generation |
| Streamlit | Rapid UI, native file upload, works in Docker |
| Azure Container Apps | Auto-scaling, managed HTTPS, secret management |

## Project structure

```
multimodal-rag/
├── app.py                          # Streamlit UI
├── config/settings.py              # Pydantic settings (env vars)
├── src/
│   ├── orchestrator.py             # Top-level coordinator
│   ├── ingestion/
│   │   ├── pdf_pipeline.py         # PyMuPDF + chunking
│   │   ├── image_pipeline.py       # GPT-4 Vision captioning
│   │   └── csv_pipeline.py         # Row serialisation
│   ├── embeddings/
│   │   └── embedding_manager.py    # OpenAI embed + Pinecone upsert
│   ├── retrieval/
│   │   ├── hybrid_retriever.py     # BM25 + semantic + RRF + Cohere rerank
│   │   └── rag_chain.py            # Prompt assembly + GPT-4o answer
│   └── evaluation/
│       └── metrics.py              # MRR, P@K, faithfulness, latency
├── Dockerfile
├── azure-deploy.bicep
└── requirements.txt
```

## Resume bullet

> Built a production-grade multi-modal RAG system using LangChain, Pinecone (namespaced
> vector store), and OpenAI text-embedding-3-large with hybrid BM25 + semantic search,
> Reciprocal Rank Fusion, and Cohere cross-encoder reranking. Supports PDFs, images
> (GPT-4 Vision captioning), and CSV data with metadata filtering, confidence scoring,
> and a real-time evaluation dashboard tracking MRR, Precision@5, and answer faithfulness.
> Containerised with Docker and deployed on Azure Container Apps with auto-scaling.